on mouseDown
  [  0] pushint16 3 ............................. <3>
  [  3] pushint16 60 ............................ <60>
  [  6] pusharglistnoret 2 ...................... <3, 60>
  [  8] extcall 12 .............................. SoundFadeOut(3, 60)
  [ 10] pusharglistnoret 0 ...................... <>
  [ 12] extcall 5 ............................... play done
  [ 14] ret
end
